song_name: I Dont Wanna Lose Your Love

version_description: From Ceremonies Remixes and Rarities. This is the complete song with full lyrics. Enjoy.
The original song is already tabed and is finger picked which might be hard for some. I tried to find the right chords to play along with the tab.
Try barre chords (5th fret). Sounds fine acoustic.

This is the chords breakdown for the Santana classic as is played on the Moonflower album. The open chords on the 1st verse are odd so they will be tabbed at the end. The chorus rhythem is odd so that will be tabbed at the end too. If you're playing guitar, the Eb can be substituted for a Cm7 at the 3rd fret. It makes for way easier fingering and sounds virtually the same.
